## API Reference

### 비밀번호

#### `Security.hashPassword(password, saltBytes?, iterations?)`
```typescript
const hash = Security.hashPassword('MyPassword123!');
// { hash, salt, iterations, algorithm }
```

#### `Security.verifyPassword(password, storedHash)`
```typescript
const valid = Security.verifyPassword('MyPassword123!', hash);
```

#### `Security.validatePasswordStrength(password)`
```typescript
const result = Security.validatePasswordStrength('weak');
// { valid: false, strength: 'weak', issues: [...] }
```

### JWT

#### `Security.createJWT(payload, secret, expiresIn?)`
```typescript
const token = Security.createJWT(
  { userId: 123, role: 'admin' },
  'secret-key',
  3600  // 1시간
);
```

#### `Security.verifyJWT(token, secret)`
```typescript
const verified = Security.verifyJWT(token.token, 'secret-key');
// { valid: true, payload: {...} }
```

### 검증

#### `Security.validateEmail(email)` | `Security.validateIPv4(ip)` | `Security.validateURL(url)` | `Security.validateUUID(uuid)` | `Security.validatePhoneNumber(phone)`

```typescript
Security.validateEmail('user@example.com');     // true
Security.validateIPv4('192.168.1.1');           // true
Security.validateURL('https://example.com');    // true
Security.validateUUID('550e8400-...');          // true
Security.validatePhoneNumber('+82101234567');   // true
```

### 정제

#### `Security.sanitizeHTML(html)` | `Security.sanitizeShellInput(input)` | `Security.escapeSQLString(str)`

```typescript
const clean = Security.sanitizeHTML('<script>alert("xss")</script>');
const safe = Security.sanitizeShellInput('rm -rf /');
const escaped = Security.escapeSQLString("'; DROP TABLE users; --");
```

### 생성

#### `Security.generateSecureToken(length?)` | `Security.generateSecureRandomInt(min, max)`

```typescript
const token = Security.generateSecureToken(32);  // 32자 토큰
const random = Security.generateSecureRandomInt(1, 100);
```

### Rate Limiting

#### `Security.createRateLimiter(maxRequests, windowMs)`

```typescript
const limiter = Security.createRateLimiter(10, 60000);  // 60초에 10개 요청

if (limiter.isAllowed(userId)) {
  // 요청 처리
} else {
  // Rate limit 초과
}
```

